org.janusgraph.graphdb.query

Interface JanusGraphPredicate

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BiPredicate<Object,Object>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AndJanusPredicate, Cmp, ConnectiveJanusPredicate, Contain, Geo, OrJanusPredicate, Text

    public interface JanusGraphPredicate
extends BiPredicate<Object,Object>
    A special kind of BiPredicate which marks all the predicates that are natively supported by JanusGraph and known to the query optimizer. Contains some custom methods that JanusGraph needs for query answering and evaluation.

    This class contains a subclass used to convert Tinkerpop's BiPredicate implementations to the corresponding JanusGraph predicates.

    Author:
    Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
